Usage: evp [--dry-run] <command> [options] [packages...]

Package Management:
  install <pkg>...           Install packages
  remove <pkg>...            Remove packages (safe: deselect + depclean)
  remove -f <pkg>...         Force remove (--unmerge, ignores deps)
